  <div class="container">
    <h1>VibeChat – Account Deletion Request</h1>
    <p>
      You can request deletion of your VibeChat account and all associated data at any time.
      Follow the instructions below to initiate the deletion process.
    </p>

    <h2>How to Request Account Deletion</h2>
    <p>To delete your account, please send an email to the support team:</p>

    <div class="email-box">
      <strong>Email:</strong> support@bizvility.com<br />
      <strong>Subject:</strong> Delete My Account<br />
      <strong>Required Info:</strong> Your registered email / phone number.
    </div>

    <h2>What Data Will Be Deleted?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Your account profile (name, email, phone)</li>
      <li>Chat history stored on server</li>
      <li>Uploaded media files</li>
      <li>Contacts saved inside VibeChat</li>
      <li>All linked device information</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What Data We May Retain Temporarily</h2>
    <p>
      For security and fraud-prevention purposes, certain logs may be retained for up to
      <strong>30 days</strong> after deletion:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>System logs</li>
      <li>Security audit logs</li>
      <li>Spam/abuse reports</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Processing Time</h2>
    <p>
      Account deletion requests are processed within <strong>7 working days</strong>.
      You will receive a confirmation email once deletion is completed.
    </p>

    <h2>Need Help?</h2>
    <p>
      If you need any assistance regarding account deletion or privacy, contact:
    </p>

    <div class="email-box">
      support@bizvility.com
    </div>

